{"TopicId":52149,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Can you land on the sun?","CreatedByName":"ckimstafu","CreatedById":92014,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-06T22:49:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ckimstafu","CreatedById":92014,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-06T22:49:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m just asking out of curiosity. Can you land on the sun, or will it burn you before you get to close? (or is it just IMPOSSIBLE?)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vexx32","CreatedById":12283,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T01:09:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThread moved to Gameplay Questions and Tutorials.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs far as I remember, there\u0027s a certain altitude where the game will just destroy your craft and say that it overheated. Not sure exactly how close you can get, though.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SRV Ron","CreatedById":69806,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T01:20:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENope;\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/mlb1m7J.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022mlb1m7J.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"staf7","CreatedById":47732,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T01:22:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SRV Ron\u0022 data-cite=\u0022SRV Ron\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENope;\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/mlb1m7J.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022mlb1m7J.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eyou do notice you were heading at 90\u0027000 M/s even if you were able to you still would have blown up\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DevoidLight","CreatedById":60164,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T04:43:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022staf7\u0022 data-cite=\u0022staf7\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eyou do notice you were heading at 90\u0027000 M/s even if you were able to you still would have blown up\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe point of the experiment was probably to see whether you could actually reach the surface at all.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sirine","CreatedById":74830,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T05:35:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/57133-Landed-on-Sun\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/57133-Landed-on-Sun\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMy craft end-up on the surface of Sun. Unintentionally.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BFGfreak","CreatedById":57395,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T06:13:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/OnOZPAs7oLw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003EIt would appear that you cannot land on a giant ball of nuclear fusion for some strange reason.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"700NitroXpress","CreatedById":90322,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T16:55:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI had the debug menu running with, infinite fuel, unbreakable joints, and the lander was coming down at 100 m/s and it still exploded. I just wish that the explosion altitude was 1337 and not some number in the 1200\u0027s.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fr8monkey","CreatedById":76199,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T20:26:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou guys are doing it wrong. You can land on the sun... you just have to do it at night.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mr Shifty","CreatedById":68146,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T20:31:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou guys are doing it wrong. You can land on the sun... you just have to do it at night.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E100% pure awesome. Plus one internets.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"A1catraz","CreatedById":90647,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T20:38:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou guys are doing it wrong. You can land on the sun... you just have to do it at night.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou realize that when the sun \u0022sets\u0022 it isn\u0027t moving, the Earth is moving. The sun is always burning, Fr8monkey; go back to school.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Smidge204","CreatedById":89677,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-11-07T20:43:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022A1catraz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022A1catraz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou realize that when the sun \u0022sets\u0022 it isn\u0027t moving, the Earth is moving. The sun is always burning, Fr8monkey; go back to school.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is what \u0022not getting the joke\u0022 looks like \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s a pretty old joke, too!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E=Smidge=\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AnatolyVasserman","CreatedById":99345,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T18:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMaybe making an actual sun interactions mechanics would be nice.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WafflesToo","CreatedById":71736,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T19:00:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022A1catraz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022A1catraz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou realize that when the sun \u0022sets\u0022 it isn\u0027t moving, the Earth is moving. The sun is always burning, Fr8monkey; go back to school.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThank you very much for proving that Poe\u0027s law is still in effect. I was a little worried there. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xxjetterxx","CreatedById":37766,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T19:05:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECrafts need to just turn into goop and fall to the sun. Get to work, Squad!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimbo Jambo","CreatedById":76960,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T19:16:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Fr8monkey\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou guys are doing it wrong. You can land on the sun... you just have to do it at night.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMight also work during a solar eclipse.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"thunderstar","CreatedById":64703,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T19:26:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022staf7\u0022 data-cite=\u0022staf7\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eyou do notice you were heading at 90\u0027000 M/s even if you were able to you still would have blown up\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ewell, make a ship capable of killing that velocity and we\u0027ll see\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CarlosMaximus","CreatedById":99289,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T23:51:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks like the North Koreans beat us all to it... \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RSwordsman","CreatedById":78678,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-25T23:56:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022A1catraz\u0022 data-cite=\u0022A1catraz\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou realize that when the sun \u0022sets\u0022 it isn\u0027t moving, the Earth is moving. The sun is always burning, Fr8monkey; go back to school.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou do realize you\u0027re trying to educate a fan of a space game here, right? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI think it would be awesome if your ship could be built to be buoyant enough to float on the sun\u0027s corona.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cerberus738","CreatedById":100744,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-26T04:30:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CarlosMaximus\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CarlosMaximus\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELooks like the North Koreans beat us all to it... \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eha ha ha ah aha ha ha way to go north Korea!! and only took 18 hours!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lightning22","CreatedById":98503,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-26T13:39:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CarlosMaximus\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CarlosMaximus\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELooks like the North Koreans beat us all to it... \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.tweaktown.com/news/35032/north-korea-confirms-it-has-landed-a-man-on-the-sun/index.html\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E:cool:\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue2.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:sticktongue:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESo how much delta V would you need to manage anything even close to that in KSP, without something like the interstellar mod?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WafflesToo","CreatedById":71736,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-26T16:09:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lightning22\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Lightning22\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESo how much delta V would you need to manage anything even close to that in KSP, without something like the interstellar mod?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEvery sun-diver I\u0027ve ever build required about 8km/s of dV and it was a 16-day trip (one way of course). I haven\u0027t got any earthly idea how much power it would take to cut the travel time down to 18-hours in KSP; let alone the ultimate realism mod \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xtremespino","CreatedById":63473,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-28T23:42:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENo, its the one thing that real life and KSP have in common \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WafflesToo","CreatedById":71736,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-29T02:23:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022xtremespino\u0022 data-cite=\u0022xtremespino\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENo, its the one thing that real life and KSP have in common \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOh come on, don\u0027t be such a stick-in-the-mud. You can land on the sun IRL... once \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xtremespino","CreatedById":63473,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-02-05T21:34:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WafflesToo\u0022 data-cite=\u0022WafflesToo\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EOh come on, don\u0027t be such a stick-in-the-mud. You can land on the sun IRL... once \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou could do a sacrificial landing, I guess. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}